name: The Changeling
overview: Apollo and Emma's love story is a fairy tale—until Emma mysteriously vanishes. Bereft, Apollo finds himself on a death-defying odyssey through a New York City he didn't know existed.

episodes.name: First Comes Love
episodes.overview: A bookseller from Queens meets a librarian from Virginia. They fall in love, marry, have a baby—and trigger an unimaginable series of events.

episodes.name: Then Comes a Baby in a Baby Carriage
episodes.overview: The exhaustion of new parenthood is taking its toll on Emma and Apollo. To make matters worse, Emma starts getting strange texts.
Emma does the unthinkable. Apollo tries to find meaning in the aftermath—and finally decides what to do with his valuable book.

episodes.name: The Wise Ones
episodes.overview: Apollo and Patrice make a sale to William Wheeler, who later gives Apollo stunning news.

episodes.name: This Woman’s Work
episodes.overview: The mysterious washerwoman’s ominous words leave a lasting impression. Apollo comes face-to-face with his true enemy.

episodes.name: Aftermath
episodes.overview: Emma finds Cal and the Wise Ones on North Brother Island, where she pieces together clues to locate a special place.

episodes.name: Stormy Weather
episodes.overview: Lillian reckons with a dark night from her past and records a message for her son, Apollo.
